{"title":"淮河风浪","authors":["贺羡泉"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":8,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"淮河风浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贺羡泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月里淮河泛大浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"层层大浪高过墙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野鸭不敢落水面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼儿忙往水底藏！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船家姑娘胆子壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把船儿驾在浪山上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个大浪扑过来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪花都飞到她身上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一阵大风刮过来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把船桅都刮得呜呜响！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘稳在船舷站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕那浪大与风狂——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"防汛的器材装满船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要连夜运往险段上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看她赶着“滚子浪”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多像赶着一群羊？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看她橹把握在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多像战士握着枪？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岸上人儿夸赞不绝口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都问这是谁家好姑娘？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何必要问姑娘名和姓？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淮河儿女，哪个不敢斗风浪！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}